{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":930,"text":"These are simple objects:"},{"time":2385,"text":"clocks, keys, combs, glasses."},{"time":6180,"text":"They are the things the victims of genocide in Bosnia"},{"time":8520,"text":"carried with them on their final journey."},{"time":11517,"text":"We are all familiar with these mundane,"},{"time":14240,"text":"everyday objects."},{"time":15974,"text":"The fact that some of the victims carried"},{"time":17559,"text":"personal items such as\ntoothpaste and a toothbrush"},{"time":20973,"text":"is a clear sign they had no idea"},{"time":23492,"text":"what was about to happen to them."},{"time":25320,"text":"Usually, they were told that they were going to be"},{"time":27711,"text":"exchanged for prisoners of war."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30199,"text":"These items have been recovered"},{"time":32212,"text":"from numerous mass graves across my homeland,"},{"time":35050,"text":"and as we speak, forensics are exhuming bodies"},{"time":37580,"text":"from newly discovered mass graves,"},{"time":39714,"text":"20 years after the war."},{"time":41250,"text":"And it is quite possibly the largest ever discovered."},{"time":45333,"text":"During the four years of conflict"},{"time":47611,"text":"that devastated the Bosnian nation in the early '90s,"},{"time":50457,"text":"approximately 30,000 citizens, mainly civilians,"},{"time":53888,"text":"went missing, presumed killed,"},{"time":55823,"text":"and another 100,000 were killed"},{"time":57803,"text":"during combat operations."},{"time":59530,"text":"Most of them were killed"},{"time":61159,"text":"either in the early days of the war"},{"time":62932,"text":"or towards the end of the hostilities,"},{"time":64298,"text":"when U.N. safe zones like Srebrenica"},{"time":67477,"text":"fell into the hands of the Serb army."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70522,"text":"The international criminal tribunal"},{"time":72640,"text":"delivered a number of sentences"},{"time":74330,"text":"for crimes against humanity and genocide."},{"time":77109,"text":"Genocide is a systematic and deliberate"},{"time":80618,"text":"destruction of a racial, political, religious"},{"time":84288,"text":"or ethnic group."},{"time":85960,"text":"As much as genocide is about killing."},{"time":88540,"text":"It is also about destroying their property,"},{"time":91561,"text":"their cultural heritage,"},{"time":93451,"text":"and ultimately the very notion that they ever existed."},{"time":96713,"text":"Genocide is not only about the killing;"},{"time":99210,"text":"it is about the denied identity."},{"time":102383,"text":"There are always traces â€”"},{"time":103813,"text":"no such thing as a perfect crime."},{"time":105532,"text":"There are always remnants of the perished ones"},{"time":108267,"text":"that are more durable than their fragile bodies"},{"time":110785,"text":"and our selective and fading memory of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114523,"text":"These items are recovered"},{"time":117180,"text":"from numerous mass graves,"},{"time":118352,"text":"and the main goal of this collection of the items"},{"time":121766,"text":"is a unique process"},{"time":123234,"text":"of identifying those who disappeared in the killings,"},{"time":126512,"text":"the first act of genocide on European soil"},{"time":129482,"text":"since the Holocaust."},{"time":130905,"text":"Not a single body should remain undiscovered"},{"time":133419,"text":"or unidentified."},{"time":135285,"text":"Once recovered,"},{"time":136650,"text":"these items that the victims carried with them"},{"time":139573,"text":"on their way to execution"},{"time":141052,"text":"are carefully cleaned, analyzed,"},{"time":143409,"text":"catalogued and stored."},{"time":145647,"text":"Thousands of artifacts are\npacked in white plastic bags"},{"time":148797,"text":"just like the ones you see on CSI."},{"time":151200,"text":"These objects are used as a forensic tool"},{"time":153938,"text":"in visual identification of the victims,"},{"time":156393,"text":"but they are also used as\nvery valuable forensic evidence"},{"time":159640,"text":"in the ongoing war crimes trials."},{"time":162477,"text":"Survivors are occasionally called"},{"time":164568,"text":"to try to identify these items physically,"},{"time":167119,"text":"but physical browsing is extremely difficult,"},{"time":170449,"text":"an ineffective and painful process."},{"time":173551,"text":"Once the forensics and doctors and lawyers"},{"time":177344,"text":"are done with these objects,"},{"time":178486,"text":"they become orphans of the narrative."},{"time":181417,"text":"Many of them get destroyed, believe it or not,"},{"time":184319,"text":"or they get simply shelved,"},{"time":185956,"text":"out of sight and out of mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188198,"text":"I decided a few years ago"},{"time":190714,"text":"to photograph every single exhumed item"},{"time":193380,"text":"in order to create a visual archive"},{"time":195281,"text":"that survivors could easily browse."},{"time":198631,"text":"As a storyteller, I like to give back to the community."},{"time":202688,"text":"I like to move beyond raising awareness."},{"time":205431,"text":"And in this case, someone may"},{"time":207615,"text":"recognize these items"},{"time":209216,"text":"or at least their photographs will remain"},{"time":211912,"text":"as a permanent, unbiased and accurate reminder"},{"time":215714,"text":"of what happened."},{"time":217626,"text":"Photography is about empathy,"},{"time":219764,"text":"and the familiarity of these\nitems guarantee empathy."},{"time":222982,"text":"In this case, I am merely a tool,"},{"time":225436,"text":"a forensic, if you like,"},{"time":227090,"text":"and the result is a photography that is as close"},{"time":229755,"text":"as possible of being a document."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232376,"text":"Once all the missing persons are identified,"},{"time":235515,"text":"only decaying bodies in their graves"},{"time":237288,"text":"and these everyday items will remain."},{"time":239630,"text":"In all their simplicity,"},{"time":241555,"text":"these items are the last testament"},{"time":243762,"text":"to the identity of the victims,"},{"time":245319,"text":"the last permanent reminder"},{"time":247347,"text":"that these people ever existed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249319,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251657,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}